 ask. Can you help me?

 let's go!

40.text:
I'm Manual! It is a twin striker who will become a hero someday! 
 Defeat GUARD ARM of Hero Ahim ... It's a legend that I wanted to do someday.

41.text:
Hello! I am a blast archer RIRI.

42.text:

 Monsters flying in the sky are troublesome opponents, but we can attack from afar.

44.text:
Hello! It is RIRI of blast archer.

 My brother's enemy! Please, please help me!

45.text:
Hello! It is RIRI of blast archer.

 <Value Type = "LocationName" ID = "FLD003_E"/>

46.text:
I ... what was it, what was the name? 
 ...... SARAH? Yes, SARAH. Yeah. 
 I'm SARAH and I have a request. 
 <Value Type = "EnemyName" ID = "E006_00_00_01001"/> I have to subdue some of them, but I can't do it by myself. 
 I'm really in trouble because I'm blocked in all directions. 
 If you like, would you help me, SARAH?

47.text:
Yeah, I'm the spellcaster SARAH. 
 ...... It's confusing. 
 This time, I want to get the ore that can be obtained by Asteria Plains and <Value Type = "EnemyName" id = "E000_00_00_01001"/>. 
 Regardless of the former, the latter will fight.

 Please help me. I'll ask.

48.text:
I'm a spellcaster SARAH. 
 Is it an Imagine that possesses SARAH? It's more and more complicated. 
 I want you to correct this state and cooperate to return your body to SARAH. 
 I want to extract the engram from a grave of a great person. 
 For our spell casters, they are like a common ancestor ... aren't you interested?

49.text:
I am Imagine who possessed the spellcaster SARAH. 
 I guess this long name can be managed. 
 This time, I want to collect my living engram, SARAH. Some of the tools used before birth were found. 
 However, both are monsters' nests. 
 You need your help. Can you ask?

50.text:
I'm Sarah, a spellcaster, I'm a slaft. 
 I was really saved by helping to collect the engram. 
 He was preparing to return to SARAH, but he didn't have much time. 
 I can't hear the SARAH voice. 
 If this is the case, SARAH's consciousness will disappear. 
 This is my last request. 
 Would you please let me know?

51.text:
Oh! I'm Musketta. nice to meet you! 
 Are you a heavy masher? Good. This exhilaration that defeats the enemy with a heavy blow! It's irresistible! 
 Alright, I'll do a lecture on the weapon of the heavy masher. 
 <Value Type = "EnemyName" ID = "E005_00_00_01001"/> Don't say you get used to it!

52.text:
You're me! Musketta. 
 How about a heavy masher training? This time, I want you to get along with my work. 
 <Value Type = "LocationName" ID = "FLD001_E"/> with <value Type = "EnemyName" id = "E000_00_00_01001"/>. Is it easy? 
 Actually, the teacher told me, "I remember cooperating with my friends." I can't do that if I'm alone. 
 I think it will be a study for me, so can you go out with me?

53.text:
You're me! Musketta. 
 I was thinking of looking for a teacher, but I heard a little disgusting story. 
 It seems that a minsterhorn child does not return while going out to "<Value Type =" LocationName "ID =" FLD001_N "/>". 
 I was taken care of by the people there, and I really don't let it go. 
 I want you to help you. Is it not good?

54.text:
You're me! Musketta. 
 I went to Larpal looking for a teacher, but there was a little fuss. 
 It's a story that the food and luggage you kept were devastated. Do you remember something ... I'm a little worried. 
 I want to go to Larpal and find out. Can you help me?

55.text:
You're me! Musketta. 
 Do you remember Larpal's luggage vandalism? It's the HIGHLAND FOX flock.

 It seems that "Sapphire TROT" was the leader for the next flock. I remember it. A long time ago, I lost!

 sorry!  Please help me!
